{"type": "article", "id": 14054, "title": "陶瓷七件套", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-27T07:48:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000331N9ioheX6AT0MfO7m.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t向来以不锈钢产品著称的丹麦设计公司 Vipp 正在扩大品牌范围，邀请了丹麦著名陶瓷制作者 Annemette Kissow 手工制作了一组陶瓷餐具，包括了碗、盘子、鸡蛋杯、牛奶壶、茶杯、咖啡杯和咖啡盘。这一套餐具共七件，采用无光的白色和灰色，像Vipp的产品一样拥有柔和光洁的品质。特别之处在于每一个餐具都被中间的一条线分成两段，形成了有起伏的曲线。<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/vipp-adds-ceramics-collection-expanding-brand/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看相关信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141700x7TNXMzvmK6qckRi.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"820\" title=\"5\" alt=\"5\" data-ratio=\"0.75925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141700kwSt2ziWo7IcvNRO.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"280\" title=\"5\" alt=\"5\" data-ratio=\"0.46666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141700wqiCFg8IHaPp1D27.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\"5\" alt=\"5\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}